- Added `analyze_judge_results()` to `improvement.py` with dimension-specific advice for all 5 judge dimensions
- Added `--judge-files` option to the `improve` CLI command, enabling mixed deterministic + judge analysis in a single report
- 22 new tests (20 unit + 2 CLI integration), 389 total, all passing, zero ruff violations

